    },
    {
      "id": "REQ-4",
      "section": "Composition de l'équipe",
      "description": "Profils des consultants mobilisés : Cloud Architect, DevOps Engineers, Security Expert, Project Manager. Certifications AWS requises.",
      "weight": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "REQ-5",
      "section": "FinOps & optimisation des coûts",
      "description": "Estimation des coûts AWS mensuels, stratégie d'optimisation (Reserved Instances, Savings Plans), reporting FinOps mensuel.",
      "weight": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "REQ-6",
      "section": "SLA & support",
      "description": "Engagement de disponibilité 99.9%, astreinte 24/7 durant la migration, support Level 2 inclus pendant 3 mois.",
